---
import artistry1 from '../assets/artistry-1.jpg';
import artistry2 from '../assets/artistry-2.jpg';
---

<section id="recent-projects" class="md:h-screen">
  <main class="space-y-12 h-full gap-10 px-10 md:flex md:justify-between md:items-center">
    <div>
      <h2
        class="text-3xl uppercase md:mb-10 sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl 2xl:8xl"
      >
        <span class="md:block">My most</span>
        <span class="md:block">recent</span>
        <span class="md:block">project</span>
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl 2xl:text-3xl"
      >
        Brand and Marketing Design
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-sm mx-auto md:max-w-96">
      <figure class="space-y-4">
        <figcaption class="text-center italic">
          Landing page for Ro-ed Logistics and Services
        </figcaption>
        <img src={artistry2.src} class="max-w-72 mx-auto md:max-h-64 lg:max-h-96" />
        <figcaption class="text-justify">
          Developed a responsive landing page that seamlessly adapts to various
          screen sizes and devices, ensuring an optimal user experience.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-12 mx-auto md:max-w-96 md:mx-0 md:flex md:flex-col md:gap-12">
      <div class="text-sm">
        <figure class="space-y-4">
          <figcaption class="text-center italic">
            Trucking Management System for Ro-Ed Logistics and Services
          </figcaption>
          <img src={artistry1.src} />
          <figcaption class="text-justify">
            Developed a user-friendly management system that can manage and
            secure trip and travel informaion efficiently.
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm">
        <figure class="space-y-4">
          <figcaption class="text-center italic">
            Simultaneous Data Compression for faster encoding and decoding using
            Huffman Algorithm
          </figcaption>
          <img src={artistry1.src} />
          <figcaption class="text-justify">
            Developed a user-friendly data compression system that provides
            efficient compression ratio and compression speed in regards with
            the time and speed of both compression and decompression.
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</section>
